549
00:33:27,790 --> 00:33:31,199
We've been struggling these last few days.

550
00:33:31,199 --> 00:33:34,960
I know it might be better if Old Lin told you this.

551
00:33:34,960 --> 00:33:36,830
But you know how he is.

552
00:33:36,830 --> 00:33:39,160
