553
00:33:39,160 --> 00:33:40,540
But I don't mind.

554
00:33:40,540 --> 00:33:42,100
I've got thick skin.

555
00:33:42,100 --> 00:33:47,160
So, with that being said, if you're not okay with it,

556
00:33:47,160 --> 00:33:48,490
