557
00:33:48,490 --> 00:33:50,500
I can handle it.

558
00:33:54,783 --> 00:33:55,834
You just started the business

559
00:33:55,834 --> 00:33:58,064
and already encountered such a situation?

560
00:33:58,750 --> 00:34:00,750
Big companies like B&amp;C Motors

561
00:34:00,750 --> 00:34:04,980
will never let startups like you get ahead.

562
00:34:06,000 --> 00:34:08,880
Since you came to me, I'll be straight with you.

563
00:34:08,880 --> 00:34:10,260
Okay.

564
00:34:12,150 --> 00:34:15,190
