577
00:34:59,920 --> 00:35:01,610
Hold on to that thought.

578
00:35:01,610 --> 00:35:04,765
Get him into Linqi Capital first.

579
00:35:04,765 --> 00:35:06,825
Don't worry. Leave it to me.

580
00:35:09,590 --> 00:35:11,340
Here's a toast to you.

581
00:35:11,340 --> 00:35:13,370
