593
00:36:45,570 --> 00:36:50,310
Look, your mom and I got both career and love going strong.

594
00:36:55,760 --> 00:36:58,230
Dad, that show doesn't work for me.

595
00:36:58,230 --> 00:37:02,930
You haven't divorced yet because you're tied up in too many ways.

596
00:37:02,930 --> 00:37:05,300
I don't want to be tied up.

597
00:37:05,300 --> 00:37:09,020
I definitely don't want to keep pretending after taking your money.

598
00:37:14,630 --> 00:37:17,610
Also, drink less, Dad.

599
00:37:17,610 --> 00:37:19,360
Get a checkup.

600
00:37:19,360 --> 00:37:21,650
Or your liver will be in trouble soon.

601
